<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=15421&amp;p=187473#p187473"><![CDATA[
&quot;Mark forums read&quot; risks missing a new post submitted between when you &quot;View unread posts&quot; and when you &quot;Mark forums read&quot;. To mark only the topic you're viewing as read, click the permanent link icon to the left of &quot;Posted:&quot; at the upper right corner of the last post in the topic.<br /><br /><img src="https://forums.nesdev.com/styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" alt="Image" /> <span style="font-size: 85%; line-height: normal"><strong>Posted:</strong> Sun Jan 22, 2017 9:20 PM</span><br /><strong>^</strong> Click this<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Sun Jan 22, 2017 6:20 pm</p><hr />
